    <item>
      <title>日产股价上涨令亚洲做空最多的汽车制造商交易员蒙受损失</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/nissan-share-rally-burns-traders-in-asia-s-most-shorted-carmaker</link>
      <description><![CDATA[对于做空日产汽车公司（亚洲做空量最大的汽车制造商）的交易员来说，这是痛苦的一周，因为在与实力更强大的竞争对手本田汽车公司进行合并谈判后，日产汽车公司的股价在两天内飙升了 30％ 以上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/nissan-share-rally-burns-traders-in-asia-s-most-shorted-carmaker</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 05:10:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储迫使亚洲做出选择：接受货币贬值或抵制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/asian-currencies-tumble-as-fed-s-hawkish-cut-jolts-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储采取强硬降息措施后，亚洲各国央行都面临着艰难的决定 — — 是采取代价高昂的措施反击美元走强，还是袖手旁观，看着本国货币贬值。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/asian-currencies-tumble-as-fed-s-hawkish-cut-jolts-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 01:12:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
